England Blanket Bog Model: predict from Biomod2 models

Crop predictor stack

do the projections

projname <- format(Sys.Date(), "%Y%m%d")
myBiomodProj <- BIOMOD_Projection(myBiomodModelOut, 
                                  new.env = predictors_new, 
                                  proj.name = paste(projname), 
                                  selected.models = "all", 
                                  binary.meth = "ROC", 
                                  build.clamping.mask = FALSE)

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-= Do Models Projections -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

    > Projecting blanket.bog_AllData_RUN1_RF ...
    > Projecting blanket.bog_AllData_RUN1_GLM ...
    > Projecting blanket.bog_AllData_Full_RF ...
    > Projecting blanket.bog_AllData_Full_GLM ...

    > Building ROC binaries
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-= Done -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
plot(myBiomodProj, str.grep = "Full_GLM")

plot(myBiomodProj, str.grep = "Full_RF")

list.files(path = paste0("../scripts/blanket.bog/proj_", projname)) #, pattern = "gri")
[1] "blanket.bog.20171206.projection.out"  "proj_20171206_blanket.bog.grd"       
[3] "proj_20171206_blanket.bog.gri"        "proj_20171206_blanket.bog_ROCbin.grd"
[5] "proj_20171206_blanket.bog_ROCbin.gri"

#write GLM to file
writeRaster(myBiomodProj@proj@val@layers[[4]], filename = "../outputs/bb_GLM_mod2a.tif", overwrite = TRUE)
#write RF to file 
writeRaster(myBiomodProj@proj@val@layers[[3]], filename = "../outputs/bb_RF_mod2a.tif", overwrite = TRUE)

ensemble it

myBiomodEF <- BIOMOD_EnsembleForecasting(projection.output = myBiomodProj, EM.output = myBiomodEM) #ensemble forecast

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-= Do Ensemble Models Projections -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

    > Projecting blanket.bog_EMcvByROC_mergedAlgo_RUN1_AllData ...
plot(wmean.ras)

export

writeRaster(wmean.ras, "../outputs/bb_EM_mod2a_wmean.tif")
